About SOY PROTEIN RESAERCH, JAPAN

This journal is a report on the results of the grant research, and is published as an annual journal under the title "SOY PROTEIN RESEARCH, JAPAN".

This is based on Nutritional Science of Soy Protein (JAPAN) (vols. 1-13) and Report of The Soy Protein Research Committe (vols. 14-18).

These have been taken over, and the full volume will be written together.
